---
name: Lyrics Mobile Formatting
description: Per-song mobile word-wrapping with auto-default based on alignment tags
type: feature
---
Mobile line wrapping char-limit:
- Default 14 chars when LRC has NO `<left>` / `<right>` alignment tags.
- Default 10 chars when LRC contains `<left>` or `<right>` (narrower lines for alignment).
- Admin can override per-song via `karaoke_data.mobile_char_limit` (range 9–40).
- Override flag (`charLimitOverriddenRef`) is set true only when admin saved an explicit value;
  otherwise the default auto-derives from `parsedLyrics.hasAlignmentTags`.
